            "use_product_description_for_question_1": false,
            "answer_1": "<h3><strong>🥩 15g High-Quality Protein</strong></h3><p>Supports muscle recovery and helps keep you full longer.*</p><h3><strong>🥕 Real Vegetable Blend</strong></h3><p>A savory mix of Mushrooms for balanced flavor and nourishment.</p><h3><strong>🔥 Only 90 Calories</strong></h3><p>Low-calorie, high-protein formula designed to support your weight goals.</p><h3><strong>🚫 No Sugar Added</strong></h3><p>Fat-free and sugar-free for clean, guilt-free nutrition.</p><h3><strong>📦 7 Single-Serve Pouches</strong></h3><p>Convenient 25g portions — easy to prepare anytime.</p>",
